theorem Topology.interior_closure_idempotent {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    interior (closure (interior (closure A))) = interior (closure A) := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  · intro x hx
    have hsubset : closure (interior (closure A)) ⊆ closure A := by
      have hIntSub : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure A := interior_subset
      exact closure_mono hIntSub
    exact (interior_mono hsubset) hx
  · intro x hx
    have hsubset : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure (interior (closure A)) := by
      intro y hy
      exact subset_closure hy
    have hOpen : IsOpen (interior (closure A)) := isOpen_interior
    have : x ∈ interior (closure (interior (closure A))) :=
      (interior_maximal hsubset hOpen) hx
    exact this

theorem Topology.interior_closure_mono {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X}
    (h : A ⊆ B) :
    interior (closure A) ⊆ interior (closure B) := by
  intro x hx
  have hsubset : closure A ⊆ closure B := closure_mono h
  exact (interior_mono hsubset) hx
